      "content_html": "\u003ch2\u003eNavigation\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API\"\u003eUnreal Engine C++ API Reference\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime\"\u003eRuntime\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine\"\u003eEngine\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine/Engine\"\u003eEngine\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eReferences\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eModule\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine\"\u003eEngine\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eHeader\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e/Engine/Source/Runtime/Engine/Classes/Engine/EngineTypes.h\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eInclude\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e#include \"Engine/EngineTypes.h\"\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eSyntax\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cpre\u003e\u003ccode\u003estruct FAttachmentTransformRules  \n\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eRemarks\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eRules for attaching components\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eVariables\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eType\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eName\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eDescription\u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/ff1d152e-69f5-42fd-af23-1d423921226e/api_variable_public.png\" alt=\"Public variable\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public variable\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003ebool\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003ebWeldSimulatedBodies\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eWhether to weld simulated bodies together when attaching\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/22fe9ad2-b424-434d-8fc6-9a3e134eda7d/api_variable_public.png\" alt=\"Public variable\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public variable\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine/Engine/EAttachmentRule\"\u003eEAttachmentRule\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eLocationRule\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eThe rule to apply to location when attaching\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/c9497152-f504-4657-ad9a-0d369a3fcc4d/api_variable_public.png\" alt=\"Public variable\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public variable\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine/Engine/EAttachmentRule\"\u003eEAttachmentRule\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eRotationRule\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eThe rule to apply to rotation when attaching\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/ec5de81d-6fd6-4958-b148-bf35c62a3901/api_variable_public.png\" alt=\"Public variable\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public variable\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine/Engine/EAttachmentRule\"\u003eEAttachmentRule\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eScaleRule\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eThe rule to apply to scale when attaching\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eConstructors\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eType\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eName\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eDescription\u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/d240934a-e98f-4a83-a6b8-b09ee8220f7e/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e \u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine/Engine/FAttachmentTransformRules/__ctor/1\"\u003eFAttachmentTransformRules\u003c/a\u003e\n (\n\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine/Engine/EAttachmentRule\"\u003eEAttachmentRule\u003c/a\u003e InRule,\u003cbr\u003e\nbool bInWeldSimulatedBodies\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e \u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/0b04c684-b9f2-4e70-9edd-1929ba6b9d0e/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e \u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine/Engine/FAttachmentTransformRules/__ctor/2\"\u003eFAttachmentTransformRules\u003c/a\u003e\n (\n\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine/Engine/EAttachmentRule\"\u003eEAttachmentRule\u003c/a\u003e InLocationRule,\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine/Engine/EAttachmentRule\"\u003eEAttachmentRule\u003c/a\u003e InRotationRule,\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine/Engine/EAttachmentRule\"\u003eEAttachmentRule\u003c/a\u003e InScaleRule,\u003cbr\u003e\nbool bInWeldSimulatedBodies\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e \u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eConstants\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eName\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eDescription\u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine/Engine/FAttachmentTransformRules/KeepRelativeTransform\"\u003eKeepRelativeTransform\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eVarious preset attachment rules.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine/Engine/FAttachmentTransformRules/KeepWorldTransform\"\u003eKeepWorldTransform\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e \u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine/Engine/FAttachmentTransformRules/SnapToTargetIncludingScale\"\u003eSnapToTargetIncludingScale\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e \u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Engine/Engine/FAttachmentTransformRules/SnapToTargetNotIncludingScale\"\u003eSnapToTargetNotIncludingScale\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e \u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n",
